Subject: [PATCH 5.8 regression fix] platform/x86: thinkpad_acpi: Revert: Use strndup_user() in dispatch_proc_write()
Date:   Tue, 14 Jul 2020 10:15:10 +0200
Message-Id: <20200714081510.6070-1-hdegoede@redhat.com>
MIME-Version: 1.0
